HEADWORD: Pork
<hw>Pork</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>porc</ets>, L.
<ets>porcus</ets> hog, pig. See <er>Farrow</er> a litter of pigs, and
cf. <er>Porcelain</er>, <er>Porpoise</er>.]</ety> <def>The flesh of
swine, fresh or salted, used for food.</def>⟦br⟧
